	   <tr><td colspan=2>Any weight carried over 14 lbs causes your AC to decrease starting at 15 lbs.&nbsp;&nbsp;The more weight you carry, the worse your AC gets.  Hope this helps<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
