	   <tr><td colspan=2>Cured silk usually sells for between 2-3pp per ac. This means that a whole set of cured silk should sell for 94-141pp.&nbsp;&nbsp;I have seen tailoring sites where people claim to have sold a set anywhere from 60-200pp.  It is expensive gear for low lvls, but some of the pieces are good enough to use until you have 200pp+ to throw down on a replacement piece and I think sometimes even good enough to use until you get into no-drop items.  A cheaper way to buy cured silk may be to find someone upgrading their gear, rather than a tailor who is making the gear for profit, or check out the merchants at the monk guild in FP - sometimes they are selling cured silk on my serveer.  Also, tailors may accept things like spider silks and HQ cat pelts in trade or in addition to some plat.<br>Good Luck<br><br>Egryn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
