t you'll see why not to)<br>those that say it doesn't go up if you are to far away this is what I came up with and the skill didn't start rolling up untill after 50  then it became alittle easier<br><br>21 I stayed at the board for two bubs in to the 21 lvl and that is where I am at now mabey I will go hunt somthing elese well see I will keep ya posted <br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
