	   <tr><td colspan=2>Tip 1: Feign Death does NOT work in a duel ;)<br><br>Tip 2: Never go into a Duel before your Mend Skill is ready to go.<br><br>Tip 3: Never go into a Duel with a Caster unless you have 1-2 Pumice stones handy to get rid of roots and snares and stuff.<br><br>Tip 4: When getting into a duel with a Caster Always equip your fastest weapons.&nbsp;&nbsp;Mossy Twig would be evil here.  And Use shurikens to try and interupt spells if you can.<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
