	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've found that goblins (at least the ones in Lake of Ill Omen) do not believe the feign death as easily as others.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>One other note.  Just for fun I pull a Sarnak into a goblin and then feign.  They hate each other so they attack until one of them dies.  One thing wierd, though, is that sometimes I get exp from finishing off the survivor and sometimes I do not.  And it doesn't seem to be based on how much hp the survivor has left.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
