	   <tr><td colspan=2>Seems to me you just had a bad group ...<br><br>Possibly you died because the rangers didn't know what the Taunt button is for.&nbsp;&nbsp;Taunting plus dealing damage should have easily moved him higher up the hate-list than your damage-dealing alone, hence causing the mob to switch to him after you've pulled it to the group ... also, in my experience, plunking an arrow into something incoming will make it switch immediately to the bowman.<br><br>I know this probably belongs in some other class' strategy guide, but I figure if you monks know this stuff, then you can train your groupmates ;)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
